      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry family using the same blood analogue and the same five nominal flow-speed combinations specified in the COU. The validation activity directly supports the intended use. However, validation activities are confined to the nominal operating envelope; relevance to off-nominal or shifted conditions is not established."
