      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test samples are independent of training data, sufficient in number (n ≥ 80), and representative of the nominal COU operating space.",
      "rationale": "120 test samples were withheld prior to any model training using stratified splitting. Sample size exceeds the MRL 2 minimum. Samples span all five nominal flow-speed bins with at least 20 replicates per bin. Test samples are drawn from the same experimental campaign as training data, ensuring statistical independence of individual measurements while preserving the same input-feature distribution. No samples from geometrically distinct devices or different fluid formulations are included."
